t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d67ef19 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d67ef19\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Its not done, until its done RIGHT!<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b6f1de elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8b6f1de\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Todd Edwards chief Handyman of tOdd-Jobs Handyman services, a proud Neighbor serving the community, is committed to providing you with outstanding service. We operate on a simple but powerful principle &#8211; if a job\u2019s not done right, we\u2019ll make it right.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">We know that caring for your home can be stressful, so we want you to feel reassured knowing that we take great pride in the work we do, and we make sure it\u2019s done to the highest standard. That\u2019s why we\u2019re proud to stand behind our work with the &#8220;Done Right!&#8221; Promise. If it\u2019s not done right, we promise to make it right.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Our business is about people. When you put your trust in us, we want you to be happy you did, so the next time you need a hand, you\u2019ll call us again.<\/span><b><\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">You can breathe easy knowing your project will be Done Right. We stand behind our workmanship, including the labor and materials we purchase for the project, with a Done Right Promise. If it was not done right, we promise to make it right. Contact me at your convenience and we will promptly be out to make it right.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e8d24ce\" data-id=\"e8d24ce\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8b559b0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8b559b0\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-96d8d7f\" data-id=\"96d8d7f\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9302a42 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"9302a42\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-37ee4ab elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"37ee4ab\"